| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4788 — Recovery Inhibition (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 319f6562-f4eb-50b7-bb69-0cf0e5552f29"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
